    "custom_liquid_NcYKFJ": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"static-reviews\">\n  <div class=\"reviews-wrap\">\n    <h2 class=\"reviews-title\">Customer Reviews</h2>\n    <p class=\"reviews-summary\">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ <strong>5.00</strong> out of 5 • Based on <strong>6 reviews</strong></p>\n\n    <div class=\"reviews-grid\">\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 1 -->\n      <article class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"review-top\">\n          <div class=\"review-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <div class=\"review-date\">12/27/2025</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-author\">60v.darren</div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-body\">\n          <p>Ive had the bgs-pro for 2 weeks. After ditching my old 52v geared hub bike (which broke gears twice and topped out at a measly 33 mph), I bought this. The sparkling dark purple paintjob looks insanely premium, high-quality materials everywhere, and it hits 40-41 mph gps. The direct-drive motor means that it’s reliable, with a punchy, linear throttle that has zero delay or jitter. It climbs up hills like a freight train. Handling is stable and agile despite the weight, the suspension is comfortable, and range is good so far in my testing.</p>\n\n          <p>I like the multi-mode headlights (yellow, white, both, or flash), and the Fardriver delivers smooth, powerful performance that's miles ahead. If you plan on riding this frequently at 30-40 mph you might want to swap out the brakes (i suggest sticking with DYISLAND and getting 4 pistons or buying Frog Wake FV4) and also swap the stock throttle grips out (they dont feel the best), but overall great bike 9.5/10, and yes from 0 there is a bit of a “lul” for a split second but this is probably just the controller sensors detecting where the motor positions are before sending full power which helps it be more reliable</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-media\">\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1766869231__bingu__original.png?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1766869231__bingu__original.png?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo\">\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 2 (not in your pasted snippet, so I’m not inventing it) -->\n      <!-- If you paste the missing 2 reviews, I’ll add them exactly. -->\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 3 -->\n      <article class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"review-top\">\n          <div class=\"review-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <div class=\"review-date\">12/02/2025</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-author\">Tony.BelowKnee</div>\n        <div class=\"review-title\">💜</div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-body\">\n          <p>Very well designed bike. Its performance is powerful. Im 5'9 170 and have verified going 41 mph on flat dirt. It handles really well on all the hills, bumps, sand, and loose gravel in my area.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-media\">\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__TjItQ58K__1764617172__1764617028169-img_20251130_125456_930__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__TjItQ58K__1764617172__1764617028169-img_20251130_125456_930__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo 1\">\n          </a>\n\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__1__454ehewE__1764617174__1764617162258-img_20251130_125456_972__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__1__454ehewE__1764617174__1764617162258-img_20251130_125456_972__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo 2\">\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 4 -->\n      <article class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"review-top\">\n          <div class=\"review-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <div class=\"review-date\">11/28/2025</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-author\">Joel Hoffman</div>\n        <div class=\"review-title\">Another Homerun from Bigniu</div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-body\">\n          <p>I was very excited to see the new bgsp was coming out, I currently have three of the bgx and I had the BG 03 so I know a little something about the company, they have amazing bikes customer service is unbeatable, the bgsp is all I thought it would be and more, very quick and Powerful great breaks great suspension such a smooth ride on a gearless hub motor that is completely silent, not to mention it's a gorgeous looking Emoto style electric bike, you won't be disappointed getting the new bgsp highly recommend this and any of the Bigniu bikes</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-media\">\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__di-p5cv0__1764315872__1000003222__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__di-p5cv0__1764315872__1000003222__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo 1\">\n          </a>\n\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438387__2__um7ANxPw__1764315875__1000003223__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438387__2__um7ANxPw__1764315875__1000003223__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo 2\">\n          </a>\n\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__1__L-OS5-se__1764315873__1000003224__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__1__L-OS5-se__1764315873__1000003224__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo 3\">\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 5 -->\n      <article class=\"review-card\">\n        <div class=\"review-top\">\n          <div class=\"review-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">★★★★★</div>\n          <div class=\"review-date\">11/26/2025</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-author\">Cuteepie</div>\n        <div class=\"review-title\">Great quality with a great price</div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-body\">\n          <p>Great quality with a great price. Nice customer service too</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"review-media\">\n          <a class=\"media-thumb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__R_UEHKQi__1764170470__1764170467966-20251119_202506__original__original.jpg?auto=format\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://judgeme.imgix.net/bigniu-bike/1765438386__0__R_UEHKQi__1764170470__1764170467966-20251119_202506__original__original.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=160\" alt=\"Customer photo\">\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .static-reviews{\n    padding: clamp(34px, 5vw, 70px) 16px;\n    background: #f7f7f7;\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Inter, Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #111;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-wrap{\n    max-width: 1120px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-title{\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px);\n    font-weight: 800;\n    letter-spacing: -0.03em;\n  }\n\n  .reviews-summary{\n    